ocre books.<br /><br />In <i>Knife of Dreams</i>, interesting things start happening again, and we start moving towards a conclusion. I'm in doubt whether that's actually a positive thing, seeing as that means this all has to end...<br /><br />Now it's up to Brandon Sanderson to determine whether this series will pass <i>A Song of Ice and Fire</i> as my second favourite fantasy.<br /><br /><b><i>Wheel of Time reviews</i>:</b><br />#1 <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/793271575" rel="nofollow noopener">
